channel.title: [639]Uncalled Attack - Power to the People
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img546.imageshack.us/img546/4596/41878990.jpg[/img][/center] [center][size=7pt]Nice banner amiright?[/size][/center]
I'm back! Hey guys, here to throw out another project because I decided to come back to MoparScape. This is the first post I decided to do ever since my return, I hope you'll like it! Now... This project I've decided to put together is turning out great, I'll obviously toss in some pictures to let you people reading this know what's all in the project and what-not. I've got some pictures now, will provide you with more in the future; that's a promise... [b]From me to you![/b] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Some Insight:[/b][/size] [i]Well, this is a Hyperion source, but made to be connected with the 639 client I'm using. So far there's not much added, though it's a development, so I just have to work hard to get everything I want/need on it. I'm working alone, this is a solo project because I'm never working with anyone on MoparScape again [I'll help you with your projects, I won't let you help me with mine]. So I hope you guys'll support me and this project![/i] [hr] [b]Supporters:[/b] [sub]To get in this list, just say you support.[/sub]
